These are Puzzles for 2x3 Level 4

.:: Puzzle 2x3-Level-4-1::.
There 3 different types of food: banana, apple, apricot
The people have 3 different jobs:  entrepreneur, videographer, security-guard
1. the person eating banana is in an even position##4
2. the entrepreneur is on the left or right of the security-guard##3
3. the entrepreneur is the person eating apple##1
4. the person eating apricot is on the far left##1
5. the videographer is the videographer##1

.:: Answer ::.
|        |      1      |      2      |     3     |
| Food   | apricot | banana | apple |
| Job    | videographer    | security-guard | entrepreneur |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 2x3-Level-4-2::.
The people have 3 different hobbies: woodworking, reading, collecting
The people use 3 different means of transport: subway, skateboard, scooter
1. the person who's hobby is woodworking is on the far right##1
2. the person driving the skateboard is in an even position##4
3. the person driving the scooter is on the left of the person who's hobby is collecting##1
4. the person driving the skateboard is the person driving the skateboard##1

.:: Answer ::.
|             |    1    |     2      |      3      |
| Hobby       | reading | collecting | woodworking |
| Transport   | scooter    | skateboard     | subway        |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 2x3-Level-4-3::.
The people have 3 different hobbies: filmmaking, chess, traveling
The people prefer 3 different music-genres: indie, d&b, rock
1. the person who's hobby is filmmaking is on the right of the fan of indie##1
2. the fan of d&b is on the left of the fan of indie##1
3. the person who's hobby is chess is in an even position##4

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1      |      2      |   3    |
| Hobby         | traveling     | chess | filmmaking |
| Music-Genre   | d&b | indie     | rock  |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 2x3-Level-4-4::.
The people perfer 3 different movie-genres: scientific, zombie, epic
The people prefer 3 different types of sport: surfing, tennis, ice-hockey
1. the person watching zombie movies is the person who's sport is tennis##1
2. the person watching scientific movies is the person who's sport is ice-hockey##1
3. the person watching zombie movies is in an even position##4
4. the person watching zombie movies is on the right of the person watching epic movies##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1     |    2    |    3     |
| Movie-Genre   | epic | zombie  | scientific  |
| Sport         | surfing  | tennis | ice-hockey |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 2x3-Level-4-5::.
The people have 3 different hobbies: sudoku, rock-climbing, traveling
There are 3 different nationalities: chinese, indian, malaysian
1. the person who's hobby is traveling is between the person who's hobby is sudoku and the chinese##2
2. the person who's hobby is rock-climbing is in an odd position##4
3. the malaysian is on the left of the chinese##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1     |     2     |    3     |
| Hobby         | sudoku   | traveling | rock-climbing    |
| Nationality   | indian | malaysian     | chinese |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 2x3-Level-4-6::.
The people have 3 different hobbies: chess, writing, board-games
The people prefer 3 different types of sport: snowboarding, basketball, baseball
1. the person who's hobby is chess is the person who's sport is basketball##1
2. the person who's sport is baseball is the person who's hobby is writing##1
3. the person who's hobby is writing is in an odd position##4
4. the person who's hobby is board-games is on the right of the person who's sport is baseball##1

.:: Answer ::.
|         |     1      |     2      |    3     |
| Hobby   | writing | board-games | chess   |
| Sport   | baseball     | snowboarding    | basketball |

