.:: Puzzle 2x3-Level-4-7::.
The people perfer 3 different movie-genres: scientific, action, western
3 different pets are kept: frog, hamster, horse
1. the person watching action movies is on the right of the person watching scientific movies##1
2. the person watching scientific movies is between the owner of the horse and the person watching western movies##2
3. the person watching scientific movies is on the left of the person watching action movies##1
4. the owner of the frog is in an even position##4

.:: Answer ::.
|               |      1       |      2      |   3    |
| Movie-Genre   | western | scientific | action |
| Pet           | hamster         | frog         | horse |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 2x3-Level-4-8::.
There 3 different types of food: pomegranate, cherry, avocado
3 different pets are kept: rabbit, lizard, cat
1. the owner of the rabbit is between the owner of the lizard and the person eating pomegranate##2
2. the owner of the cat is in an odd position##4
3. the owner of the lizard is on the left of the person eating avocado##1

.:: Answer ::.
|        |   1    |  2   |     3     |
| Food   | cherry | avocado | pomegranate |
| Pet    | lizard    | rabbit | cat     |

