.:: Puzzle 2x3-Level-4-9::.
The people prefer 3 different music-genres: house, rock, indie
The people prefer 3 different types of sport: sailing, water-polo, soccer
1. the person who's sport is soccer is in an odd position##4
2. the person who's sport is water-polo is on the left of the fan of house##1
3. the person who's sport is soccer is on the left of the fan of rock##1
4. the person who's sport is soccer is on the left or right of the person who's sport is water-polo##3

.:: Answer ::.
|               |   1    |    2     |    3     |
| Music-Genre   | indie   | rock  | house  |
| Sport         | soccer | water-polo | sailing |

