.:: Puzzle 2x3-Level-4-10::.
There are 3 different favourite beverages: tea, juice, sprite
There 3 different types of food: cranberry, watermelon, pomegranate
1. the person eating cranberry is on the right of the person drinking sprite##1
2. the person eating pomegranate is in an even position##4
3. the person eating pomegranate is on the right of the person drinking tea##1

.:: Answer ::.
|            |   1    |     2     |   3    |
| Beverage   | tea    | sprite      | juice |
| Food       | watermelon | pomegranate | cranberry   |

