.:: Puzzle 2x3-Level-4-14::.
The people have 3 different hobbies: camping, gardening, cooking
3 different pets are kept: cat, frog, hamster
1. the person who's hobby is cooking is between the person who's hobby is gardening and the owner of the frog##2
2. the person who's hobby is gardening is in an odd position##4
3. the owner of the frog is on the far left or far right##3
4. the person who's hobby is cooking is on the right of the owner of the cat##1

.:: Answer ::.
|         |      1      |    2    |   3    |
| Hobby   | gardening | cooking | camping |
| Pet     | cat    | hamster  | frog   |

