.:: Puzzle 2x3-Level-4-15::.
The people perfer 3 different movie-genres: crime, action, sports
The people prefer 3 different music-genres: blues, pop, techno
1. the person watching sports movies is on the right of the person watching crime movies##1
2. the fan of pop is on the left of the fan of blues##1
3. the fan of pop is on the left or right of the person watching sports movies##3
4. the person watching sports movies is in an even position##4

.:: Answer ::.
|               |    1    |    2    |    3    |
| Movie-Genre   | crime  | sports     | action |
| Music-Genre   | pop | blues | techno    |

