.:: Puzzle 2x3-Level-4-18::.
The people have 3 different hobbies: filmmaking, skydiving, writing
The people prefer 3 different music-genres: reggae, rock, disco
1. the fan of disco is on the right of the person who's hobby is filmmaking##1
2. the person who's hobby is filmmaking is in the middle##1
3. the person who's hobby is writing is the fan of rock##1
4. the fan of reggae is in an even position##4

.:: Answer ::.
|               |   1    |     2     |     3     |
| Hobby         | writing | filmmaking   | skydiving |
| Music-Genre   | rock   | reggae | disco      |

