There are 3 different nationalities: indonesian, indian, british
1. the british is on the left or right of the person drinking milk##3
2. the person drinking milk is in an odd position##4
3. the person drinking fanta is on the right of the person drinking sprite##1
4. the person drinking sprite is on the left of the indonesian##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |      1      |       2       |    3     |
| Beverage      | milk | sprite | fanta |
| Nationality   | indian   | british          | indonesian |

